description:
Reliably rugged, these overalls are handy when spending weeks in the backcountry or getting your chores done. At the end of the day, they are at home sitting around a fire with your favourite brew.Burly nylon with a bit of stretch stands up to camp life.PFC-free DWR finish sheds mist and mud.Double-layer fabric on knees for extra durability.Full-zip fly with button closure.Gusseted crotch gives you full range of motion.

